# Your rule content

- All python files shoud be formatted according to PEP8
- Especially lines should not be longer than 79 characters
- Especially there should be one empty lines for each function definitions
- Especially there should not be empty lines with blank or tab characters.
- Remove all blanks in lines that do not have any other characters.

